name: Blue Dream
description: A potent cross between Blueberry and Haze, Blue Dream balances full-body relaxation with gentle cerebral invigoration.

name: Granddaddy Purple
description: Famous for its deep purple bloom, this strain is a staple for those seeking deep relaxation and sleep aid.

name: Jack Herer
description: Named after the cannabis activist, this strain captures both cerebral elevation and heavy resin production.

name: OG Kush
description: The backbone of West Coast cannabis varieties, OG Kush is cherished for its ability to crush stress under the weight of its heavy euphoria.

name: Sour Diesel
description: A fast-acting strain known for its pungent, diesel-like aroma. It provides dreamy, cerebral effects that are long-lasting.

name: Gelato
description: A cross between Sunset Sherbet and Thin Mint GSC, known for its dessert-like aroma and heavy-handed physical relaxation.

name: Wedding Cake
description: Rich and tangy with earthy pepper flavors, this strain provides a relaxing and euphoric high that calms the body and mind.

name: Purple Haze
description: Popularized by Jimi Hendrix's 1967 classic, this strain delivers a dreamy burst of euphoria that brings veteran consumers back to their psychedelic heyday.

name: Northern Lights
description: A pure indica cherished for its resinous buds, pungently sweet, spicy aromas, and muscle-relaxing effects.

name: Girl Scout Cookies (GSC)
description: GSC typically offers waves of full-body relaxation paired with time-bending cerebral effects.

name: Pineapple Express
description: Made famous by the movie, this strain combines the potent and flavorful forces of parent strains Trainwreck and Hawaiian.

name: Durban Poison
description: This pure sativa originates from the South African port city of Durban. It has gained popularity worldwide for its sweet smell and energetic, uplifting effects.

name: Bubba Kush
description: Bubba Kush is known for its heavy tranquilizing effects. Sweet hashish flavors with subtle notes of chocolate and coffee come through on the exhale.

name: White Widow
description: Among the most famous strains worldwide, White Widow is a balanced hybrid first bred in the Netherlands by Green House Seeds.

name: Super Lemon Haze
description: A kief-caked multi-colored wonder with a tart, zesty lemon flavor and aroma. Verify uplifting and energetic.
